rows.label: tev014401_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Ryo about conditions in NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Ryo if he's heard any interesting rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Ryo about the infrastructure of NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0001
rows.name:
I know what you're thinking: "If the roads aren't
finished and the city's only half built, then what the
hell have the construction teams been doing?"[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0002
rows.name:
I assure you, we've been working our asses off
expanding and maintaining the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0003
rows.name:
But it's a pretty big job. The xenos took a city
that was intended to be completed inside the
White Whale and dumped it onto this rock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0004
rows.name:
It's not easy to build out a city without the large-scale
construction units that went down with the Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0005
rows.name:
Not to mention that we still can't get the resources we
need to do our jobs! ...Anyway, I know it's a pain,
but you'll just have to bear with us for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0008
rows.name:
I hear they're looking for candidates to try out new
weapons at the Outfitters test hangar over there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0009
rows.name:
Sounds like they're searching for some real strong
fighters.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0010
rows.name:
I don't know what they're gonna have them do,
but if you're confident in your skills, why not go
see what it entails?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0011
rows.name:
You might be able to get your hands on some new
weapons and Skells before they go on sale to the
rest of the grunts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0019
rows.name:
I was bracing for the worst after that enemy attack,
but I should have had more faith.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0020
rows.name:
After all, New LA was built aboard the finest ship in
the Earthlife Colonization Project's fleet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0021
rows.name:
Despite all the shelling we took, everything survived
without a scratch, and there was barely any damage
that required our attention.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0022
rows.name:
So now instead of wasting time on repairs, we can
get back to work on the unfinished parts of the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0023
rows.name:
We're gonna find a way to erect buildings that'll put
the ones made with the White Whale's construction
units to shame.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Ryo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0024
rows.name: That Celica girl came by again to check on Rock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0025
rows.name:
She always seems so worried that he'll have trouble
adjusting to a new job in an unfamiliar place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0026
rows.name:
But I think SHE'S the one having trouble adjusting!
Don't you think it's a little overprotective the way
she's always hovering around him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0027
rows.name:
He's a part of the construction team now.
She needs to start treating him like an adult.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Ryo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0028
rows.name:
Believe it or not, Rock's actually started smarting
off to Celica a little bit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0029
rows.name:
I heard him tell her, "You don't need to keep coming
around to check on me. Concentrate on your own
work!"[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0030
rows.name:
Anyway, the guy's got a point. He could be a little
immature when he first started, but he's grown up
a lot since then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0031
rows.name:
Celica hasn't come around as much since he said that.
I kinda miss seeing her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014401_MSG0032
rows.name:
Maybe I'm gonna have to start going for visits over at
her place...[ST:wait ]
